    "author_association": "COLLABORATOR",
    "body": "Hello @lawweiliang \r\n\r\nLets consider this exact function:\r\n- The balance before transfer is stored on line 30: `senderBalance = _balances[sender];`\r\n- We check that the balance is enough to perform on line 31: `require(senderBalance >= amount);`\r\n- At this point we know for sure that `senderBalance - amount` is greater or equal to 0, and we have thus ruled out any risk of overflow. We thus don't need solidity to perform math checks here.",
